entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You defeated a camp of gunrunners outside of Mos Eisley. Maybe now they'll peddle their wares somewhere else.
entries.journal_entry_description: Go to the camp of gunrunners outside of Mos Eisley and convince them to peddle their weapons elsewhere.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Run the gunrunners out of the area and convince them to peddle their guns elsewhere.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Return to Peawp R'dawc and let her know you fought the gunrunners.
